Text: I hope this has proper English, not American.
You would be speaking German if it wasn't for America.

I thought I was downloading episodes of Little Einsteins.  I didn't know it was one of those interactive DVD games that you use the DVD remote to play.  I'll burn it to disk and see if my 2 year old will like it.  Thanks for the upload and thank you seeders.

At least there's a bonus episode of Handy Manny - Time Out on it.
